title: Rare! 2-bed up unit in desirable Westpark w/parking; Avail 9/1
map_address: 3277 Rocky River Dr. near Edgecliff & Munn Avenues
posting_body: ['Gorgeous upstairs, second-floor unit of a high-quality, 2-family home.', 'Professionally updated and recently remodeled!', 'Beautifully maintained.', 'Hardwood floors in kitchen, dining, and living rooms.', 'Clean carpeting in the rest of the apartment with newer windows and a solid brick exterior.', 'Two bedrooms plus one extra bonus room (office, study, den, TV/reading room, playroom) off the second bedroom.', 'Living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen, one bathroom.', 'Kitchen appliances stay, including a new dishwasher and disposal, plus a built-in wine rack.', 'New Nest thermostat.', 'Loads of storage.', 'Your own newer, non-shared washer and dryer in the basement with room for extra storage.', 'Deep manicured back yard with large deck.', 'New driveway.', 'Detached garage with electric door opener and parking for 1 spot.', "Wonderful location in highly desirable West Park neighborhood near Kamm's Shopping Plaza, Fairview Hospital, schools (Our Lady of Angels, St. Joseph's Academy, St. Mark's), airport, I-90, Lakewood, Rocky River, and Metroparks.", 'Also close to several churches and libraries.', 'Tenant responsible for all utilities, including water and sewer.', 'ABSOLUTELY NO PETS (only exception: service animal).', 'NO SMOKING.', 'Sorry, no Section 8 vouchers.', 'Minimum credit score: 675.', 'Subject to background check.', "First month's rent, last month's rent, and security deposit all due upon signing.", 'Tours by appointment only.', 'Available Sept. 1, 2022!']
